## [2026-06-19 21:35 +0530] PIPELINE v1 — Initial Multi-Modal Evidence Review Pipeline
### Action
Built the first end-to-end pipeline: ClaimParser → VisionAnalyzer (Gemini lite) → EvidenceChecker → RuleEngine → RiskAnalyzer → DecisionAgent → OutputValidator. Integrated image preprocessing, safe CSV reading, and config management.
### Result
Pipeline processed all 44 test claims. Initial evaluation on 20 sample claims: 0% accuracy — all claims predicted as "not_enough_information" due to conservative fallback behavior. Gemini API integrated with retry logic. Files created: claim_parser.py, claim_processor.py, config.py, decision_agent.py, evidence_checker.py, image_preprocessor.py, output_validator.py, risk_analyzer.py, rule_engine.py, severity_engine.py, text_detector.py, utils.py, vision_analyzer.py, submission_critic.py, evaluation/main.py.
### AI Assistance
AI-assisted implementation — full pipeline skeleton generated and iteratively refined.
