## [2026-06-20 01:54 +0530] PHASE 2 — 95% Static Accuracy Achieved
### Action
Major pipeline overhaul: refined Gemini prompt for structured JSON output, improved rule engine mapping, enhanced severity detection, and added evidence standard evaluation. Implemented per-image assessment with damage type and object part detection.
### Result
Static accuracy reached 95%. Most claims correctly classified as supported/contradicted/not_enough_information. Remaining gaps in risk flag accuracy and image validation edge cases.
